    "Body": " Management Assistant The Company: We are a decentralized ICO Venture Capital Fund investing in disruptive Blockchain/Crypto projects. We provide companies with $0.5M - $1.5M in venture capital financing, Blockchain incubation and global compliant ICO execution. In doing so we provide trust, confidence and recurring income to ICO crowd investors for their investments in scalable blockchain projects. The Role: We are recruiting for a Management Assistant who is highly organized, a forward planner and is able to work effectively and independently within a demanding environment of a fast growing business. The candidate will gain the opportunity to understand all aspects of operations within the company such as HR, Marketing and Business Development in an entrepreneurial environment. Your Responsibilities: \u2022 Work with the CMO on daily operative tasks. \u2022 Perform administrative, organizational and logistical tasks. \u2022 Support with HR tasks (recruiting, searching, job postings, screening candidates) \u2022 Manage travel agendas, bookings, iteneraries, calendar, meetings, interviews. \u2022 Manage invoices, expense receipts. \u2022 Manage communications with different parties. \u2022 Perform online search and manage excel sheets. \u2022 Update documents, write content, prepare memos and presentations. \u2022 Translate text, emails and conversations from English-Hungarian-English. Requirements: \u2022 University degree \u2022 Track record of previous executive (CEO) assistant or office management work. \u2022 Highly structured, organized, efficient, super fast and strong multi-tasker! \u2022 Confident to handle pressure in a super fast-paced environment. \u2022 Motivated and driven to work independently with minimal guidance. \u2022 Excellent skills in word processing, spreadsheet, powerpoint, online search. \u2022 Must have the ability to work under pressure and work to deadlines. \u2022 Ability to work with minimal guidance and demonstrate self-starter qualities. \u2022 Excellent written & spoken communication (bilingual English & Hungarian) Why join CentrumCoin? \u2022 Be a part of the Crypto/Blockchain and ICO Revolution. \u2022 Work with highly intelligent and driven people who display a high degree of initiative, motivation and flexibility. \u2022 Work in an entrepreneurial setting that supports openness to innovative ideas. \u2022 Get exposure to various career opportunities within the organization. The position can be based either in Budapest or Moscow. Remote also possible. Apply Now! Send your CV and Cover Letter by email to [email????????????protected] with the subject line \"Management Assistant\" and state why you're best suited for the job. We are looking to hire immediately. Learn more about CentrumCoin via our website: www.centrumcoin.com Skills strong multi-tasker, word processing, spreadsheet, powerpoint, online search Compensation 2k-4k EUR ", 
